      "description": "The fics that transcend their source material.",
      "curatorId": "zorian",
      "curatorNote": "These aren't just good fanfics—they're good stories. Each one stands on its own craft: precise prose, complete narrative arcs, and characters that feel alive beyond canon. Some rewrite Taylor's fate entirely. Others illuminate corners of Earth Bet Wildbow only hinted at. If you want to know what Worm fanfiction can truly become, start here.",
      "curatorNoteCN": "这不是\"还不错的同人\"——这是真正成立的好故事。每一本都靠硬实力站稳：克制而精准的文笔、完整闭合的叙事弧、比原作更鲜活的角色生命力。有的彻底改写Taylor的命运线，有的照亮Wildbow只一笔带过的世界角落。如果你想看看Worm同人真正能走到什么高度，从这里开始。",
